description: Lists progress update streams associated with the user account making this call.

nested_items.name: ProgressUpdateStreamSummaryList
nested_items.description: List of progress update streams up to the max number of results passed in the input.

nested_items.name: ProgressUpdateStreamName
nested_items.description: The name of the ProgressUpdateStream. Do not store personal data in this field.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are more streams created than the max result, return the next token to be passed to the next call as a bookmark of where to start from.
